# Produse catalog cards

The `/produse` product grid uses **`ProduseCatalogProductCard`** (not `HorizontalCatalogProductCard`). Home and related products keep the old horizontal card.

## Page grid

- `grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 items-stretch gap-[18px]`
- Skeleton: `ProduseCatalogProductCardSkeleton`

## Card layout (2 columns inside card)

- **Container queries**: `@container` wrapper; side-by-side from `@min-[360px]`
- **Grid**: `@min-[360px]:grid-cols-[minmax(0,48%)_minmax(0,1fr)]` — image **48%**, details **52%**
- **Background**: card + image area both `#f7f7f7` (`bg-[#f7f7f7]`)
- **Border**: `border-[#e8eaf0]`, `rounded-2xl`
- **Hover**: `shadow-none transition-shadow duration-200 hover:shadow-lg` (same as HomeFeaturesGrid / product benefit cards)
- **Click**: whole card navigates to product details (`role="link"`, Enter/Space supported)

## Left column (image)

- Min height: `230px` / `@min-[360px]:260px`
- Image max height: `200px` / `@min-[360px]:230px`, `object-contain`
- Overlays: stock + delivery chips (top-left), kWh badge (bottom-left, ink `#0f1422`)

## Right column (details + price)

- **Title** + **spec line only** — no product description, subtitle, or overview
- Spec text: `[specLine1, specLine2].filter(≠ '—').join(' · ')`
- Feature pills: transport, instalare, reduceri (below specs)
- Price block at bottom: label, gross price, net line (`catalogNetPriceLine`)
- **No** add-to-cart button, **no** „Vezi detalii” link, **no** divider above price
- Industrial no-price: „La cerere” + **Cere ofertă** button only (`stopPropagation` on button)

## i18n (`produse.ts`)

Card labels: `pretLabel`, `catalogRequestQuote`, `catalogPriceOnRequest`, `catalogPriceOnRequestNote`, `catalogNetPriceLine`

## Do not change without explicit request

- 48% image column width
- `#f7f7f7` backgrounds
- 2-up page grid on `sm+`
- Click-to-details on card (no cart CTA on listing)
